Titolo: Trackmania (2020 video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Trackmania is a racing video game developed by Ubisoft Nadeo and published by Ubisoft, and is part of the TrackMania series. It was released on July 1, 2020, for Windows. A remake of TrackMania Nations, it was given the soft reboot title of Trackmania. The base game is free-to-play, with additional content available with a paid subscription model, including an in-game track editor, online events and car customization.The game has received mixed to positive reviews, with the gameplay being received positively, and its subscription model being criticized.